dct_title_s: City of Brisbane as constituted under "The City of Brisbane Acts of 1924-44"
dct_description_sm: Street map of the City of Brisbane, with relief shown by hachures. "Note: All land lying below high water mark on both banks of the Brisbane River, and of any other river, creek or stream is excluded from the City of Brisbane Area (G.G. 8th December, 1944). The boundary of the City of Brisbane from Tingalpa Creek to the Pine River is low water mark." Crown Copyright Reserved.
dct_publisher_sm: Brisbane : Survey Office, Dept. of Public Lands, 1962.
